text: Uglješići is a village in Vogošća municipality, near Sarajevo, Federation of Bosnia and Herzegovina, Bosnia and Herzegovina. ==Population== ===Ethnic composition, 1991 census=== total: 367 * Muslims by nationality - 348 (94.82%) * "Yugoslavs" - 12 (3.26%) * Serbs - 5 (1.36%) * Croats - 1 (0.27%) * others and unknown - 1 (0.27%) ==History== ==References== * Official results from the book: Ethnic composition of Bosnia-Herzegovina population, by municipalities and settlements, 1991. census, Zavod za statistiku Bosne i Hercegovine - Bilten no.234, Sarajevo 1991. title: Uglješići
